data.description: Two properties in one! This almost 4,000 sq ft.  is a great opportunity for retail with apts. above! Close by shopping center and easy access to 95 & 895. Main level is a large open area w/ 1 full bath and roughed in for a  half bath. Upstairs has separate entrance 5 offices/ bedrooms, a full bath, and a rough in for a second full bath. Convenient to local shops, restaurants and downtown. Great income producing property that won't last long!
